reviews.review_text: Cal Expo Rex shows! I remember this show well.  Pharoah Sanders (who?) opened for this Rex show.  Was hanging out, about 10' infront of the board on Jerry's side. I recall stretching out on the grass and snoozing for a bit of Pharoah's set.  The SOTM is awesome!!  I fondly remember dancin' with the love of my life... while my wife was off at RockMed getting aspirin for her 'headache'.  Both those women were trouble!  Fun, but trouble!
